  <front>
   <head>Madrigali inediti - CXV</head>
  </front>
  <body>
   <lg xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" type="poem">
    <lg n="1">
     <l n="1">In croce pendi, o gloria,</l>
     <l n="2">e dura morte, ahi pur dolce mia vita;</l>
     <l n="3">ma qual da morte or vita,</l>
     <l n="4">qual da croce ecco or gloria?</l>
     <l n="5">O viva gloria, o gloriosa vita.</l>
    </lg>
   </lg>
